{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund the building of 1500 artificial sports pitches by start of 2027",
        "additional_details": "I believe that participation in sports like football is decreasing due to poor quality pitches. To combat this we should build artificial 3G and 4G pitches for football. which could be also for rugby. We think this could increase participation in sport.",
        "background": "We want the Government to fund and build good quality football pitches for communities. ",
